detail_desc: Set with a sleeveless top, pair of puff pants and hairband in a cotton weave. Top with a wide flounce at the top and tie-top shoulder straps. Puff pants with elastication and a small frill trim at the waist and hems. Hairband with a decorative knot detail at the front and covered elastication at the back.

Sleeveless dress in a patterned cotton weave with a wrapover fastening and small opening at the back, and an elasticated seam at the waist. Lined at the top. Matching hairband with a sewn-on bow at the front and covered elastication at the back.
